cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the visualization of conversations, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and data visualization (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential for cyberpsychology (cs.CY) in understanding online conversations.
